{"tid":1977447,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家幫幫手做一做份問卷唔該","createTime":"2020-04-18T03:44:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T04:04:12.000Z","uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3185e44b31f53f4af998a2b8822565162b425a13","tid":1977447,"uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:44:11.000Z","msg":"您好! 我是理工大學應用社會科學教授呂青湖的助理，現在進行一項有關抗爭與移民的研究。目的是理解香港人如何應對政治動盪。當中會問及有關您的政治立場、對最近發生「反送中」運動的想法、以及移民海外的可能性。不論您的立場是支持、反對、不關心、或不了解抗爭運動，都希望您能填寫這份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此問卷大約需時15-20分鐘。受訪者年齡必須是18至65歲，香港永久居民，並且現居在香港。我們不會問及你個人或其他人參與抗爭的內容細節。此研究無需要您的個人資料(請不要留下名字, 身份証號碼等)。所有收集的資料只作研究用途。<br />\n<br />\n問卷限額為1000人。完成問卷後會得到$50百佳現金券。如果您同意參與, 請入：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com%2Fjfe%2Fform%2FSV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppepo9Jm%2BrpizTNr1X5Fgg%2Fao%3D&h=901ba897\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkpuhealthandsocial.au1.qualtrics.com/jfe/form/SV_1TXv4LKHLSPBosR</a>"},{"pid":"2c45adb1cface8a2400be1e517da46dfca389184","tid":1977447,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"個prof. 叫你用internet survey做data gathering ?"},{"pid":"23de5531e371f88e9aece301e795c3f8c7c56489","tid":1977447,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"自爆 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96515e5704227b1eb0b8e870e20e11898c3740c","tid":1977447,"uid":354510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c45adb1cface8a2400be1e517da46dfca389184","tid":1977447,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:45:55.000Z","msg":"個prof. 叫你用internet survey做data gathering ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"我係助理,負責幫手係各群組share條link出去俾大家做,data既野只有教授會睇到"},{"pid":"f7ee84e3418598b6